title: Hangouts 5.0 Update Rolling Out to Google Play
text:
Hangouts 5.0 Update Rolling Out to Google Play 
Published By: Droid-Life.com - Today 
Hangouts 4.0 has not been around all too long, but today, Google is slowly starting to roll out Hangouts 5.0 for all through Google Play....
